<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-5917] NoSuchMethodError when calling YamlConfigurationLoader.loadConfig()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5917</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi, when this method is called, I see this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: org.yaml.snakeyaml.Yaml.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(Lorg/yaml/snakeyaml/constructor/BaseConstructor;)V&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.cassandra.config.YamlConfigurationLoader.loadConfig(YamlConfigurationLoader.java:86)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.cassandra.config.DatabaseDescriptor.loadConfig(DatabaseDescriptor.java:125)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.cassandra.config.DatabaseDescriptor.&amp;lt;clinit&amp;gt;(DatabaseDescriptor.java:101)&lt;br/&gt;
......&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I believe it&apos;s because of an enhancement made in ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5606&quot; title=&quot;remove some deprecations in use of SnakeYaml&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5606&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5606&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The version of snakeyaml that 2.0.0-rc1 depends on is 1.6, but this constructor doesn&apos;t exist in that version but it does in version 1.12.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Coincidentally &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5317&quot; title=&quot;upgrade to recent snakeyaml&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5317&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5317&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; speaks of upgrading the snakeyaml dependency, but I&apos;m not sure what was upgraded. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Linux&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
